{"tid":255971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"看uber事件，香港因為黑警倒退到文革時期","createTime":"2017-05-24T07:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T09:01:21.000Z","uid":100916,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d00ed83cc5ce37818ae857d8aa689a8a03c461d","tid":255971,"uid":100916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:53:51.000Z","msg":"警打擊Uber拘21男女<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170523/s00001/1495512209479\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170523%2Fs00001%2F1495512209479&d=aH8KaMvKRe05vg3cyv5gNnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6f9cbef2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170523%2Fs00001%2F1495512209479&h=2bb2e043\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170523/s00001/1495512209479</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家知唔知乜野叫文革，唔知既人可以睇經典文革電影《芙蓉鎮》。故事講述女主角豆腐西施勤力賺錢，得罪一些小人，於是被定義為富農，辛苦買既屋，辛苦賺既錢被充公，然後再推去掃街。<br />\n<br />\n現在香港其實發生緊一樣既事。你用新少少既方法賺錢，捉唔到大賊既廢柴黑警就會搞9你，將你既車收走，說是犯罪工具，將你辛苦賺既錢先凍結再充公，說是犯罪得益，最後再罰你社會服務令，推你去掃地。<br />\n<br />\n大陸已經改革開放了幾十年，冇估到香港竟然走回頭路，為的是黑警做show,好似破大案咁，以為咁就可以提升警隊形象。兩岸三地，就只有香港黑警咁用力打擊uber, 何其好笑。"},{"pid":"a61c4e6cd1d43d50a51c1e00dc7a98ddaea3833c","tid":255971,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T07:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdbeaf52216fef98bd00ff7b849c9fa26571a5f2","tid":255971,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:00:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cede5ad98b9fa576978e6e23c30b0e2f1cc3548","tid":255971,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027ac803f85fb8c7011d749a0ff2c7e930b481c4","tid":255971,"uid":498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:46:47.000Z","msg":"捉非法賽車又唔見一連拉三十部之後遊街<br />\n黑警真係廢到冇人有"},{"pid":"fe650aa991e19beddbd49119b30891daa2539345","tid":255971,"uid":100916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:56:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捉非法賽車又唔見一連拉三十部之後遊街<br />\n黑警真係廢到冇人有</blockquote><br />\n佢地大事做唔到，就只有搞市民"},{"pid":"99470639ff6c484f864426c73c9f8ec1cd2267bf","tid":255971,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T08:56:35.000Z","msg":"香港一向是行政主導的貿易城市，社會經濟生活完全倚靠官僚機構的能力和信用維持。官僚機構公開放棄信用，承擔政治審查的任務，說明香港的繁榮穩定已經押上了賭桌，不再構成天經地義的共同底線。從員警和公務員到法官和廉政公署，路途並不遙遠。<span style=\"color: red;\">未來的香港特區政府和司法系統將會愈來愈接近1940年代的上海工部局，聽任自由資本主義和法治的天堂淪為地下黨和黑幫的戰場</span>。社會的極化和中產階級的流亡將會加速進行"},{"pid":"7fc30e2902e7abbd5e0bca2d5b10f0eb70899bee","tid":255971,"uid":4575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:00:35.000Z","msg":"香港邊個多的士？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係豬豬"},{"pid":"cdb13b6259319e21f2828fe716ed8e87939816ae","tid":255971,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T09:01:21.000Z","msg":"又如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}